snippet: Le’Veon Bell ran for a career-high 210 yards and 2 touchdowns, including the winner with 8 minutes 12 seconds left, in No. 13 Michigan State’s 17-13 win over No. 24 Boise State in East Lansing, Mich.
abstract: Michigan State defeats Boise State, 17-13, in college football.
